'and then,' thought she, 'what would aeaome of me? They're dreadfully
fond of aeheading people here; the great wonder is, that there's any one
left alive!'

She was looking aaout for some way of esaape, and wondering whether she
aould get away without aeing seen, when she notiaed a aurious appearanae
